question: Are there marketing materials that explain how Pennie is replacing HealthCare.gov?
text:
Are there marketing materials that explain how Pennie is replacing HealthCare.gov?
          
        
YES, the information needed to market Pennie effectively will be available in the Open Enrollment Tool. Once completed, you will find that in the 
Assister/Broker Resources
 link in the footer of pennie.com. Please also download the 
Brand Guide
 so that you are following all necessary steps to stay brand compliant. Please send any questions regarding the Pennie branding to Chachi Angelo, MarComm Manager, at 
ChaAngelo@pa.gov
.
